In Kaziranga National Park, several of the 120 tank rhinoceros died from landslides.
They are protected and considered to be endangered by extinction.
This year, the floods are particularly bad, which scientists have brought back to climate change.
Bangladesh is one of the countries most hit by global warming, according to the United Nations.
New apartments are empty
