Greta Thunberg spoke about her meeting with US President Donald Trump.
Greta Thunberg was a guest on Stephen Colbert's well-known latenight show and revealed in an interview what she had in mind when she met Donald Trump.
Climate Atticist Greta Thunberg was a guest on a popular US latenight show via video switch.
Among other things, she told us about her fight against the world's powerful.
The teenage girl also talked about her famous "bad look" in her encounter with Donald Trump.
